    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚发展债券在信心测试中吸引强劲需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kenya-s-development-bond-sale-will-be-key-market-confidence-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在反政府抗议浪潮导致当局放弃一项关键的增税计划之后，肯尼亚发售的基础设施债券吸引了强劲需求，这是对投资者兴趣的一次重要考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/kenya-s-development-bond-sale-will-be-key-market-confidence-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
